<div class="container">
  <div class="row align-items-start" style="border:1px solid red">
    <div class="col-12" style="border:1px solid blue">
      <h3>Login to Book Nest</h3>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row align-items-start" style="border:1px solid red">

    {{! <div class="col-12" style="border:1px solid purple">
      <p> test test</p>
    </div> }}

    <div class="col-12 col-lg-6" style="border:1px solid blue">
      <p>If you are an existing Book Nest user, please log in using the form
        below.</p>
      <form>
        <div class="mb-3">
          <label for="email-login" class="form-label">Email address:</label>
          <input id="email-login" type="email" class="form-control" />
        </div>
        <div class="mb-3">
          <label for="password-login" class="form-label">Password:</label>
          <input id="password-login" type="password" class="form-control" />
        </div>
        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Log In</button>
      </form>
    </div>

    <div class="col-12 col-lg-6" style="border:1px solid blue">
      <p>Book Nest is a wonderful community for those who love to read. Add
        books to your reading list and check them out to read, or share a book
        to the Book Nest app and watch our library grow!</p>

      <p>If you are a new user, don't fret! Becoming a Book Nest user is simple
        and free.</p>

      <p><a href="/signup">Click here to get an account on Book Nest!</a></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>